title: Hour 2: Fly Eagles Fly
description:
The Get Up/First Take crossover special continues. Stephen A. is loving the Cowboys loss to the Eagles. Mike Greenberg thinks Patrick Mahomes doesn't have enough to beat Buffalo. Plus the Playmaker Michael Irvin reveals his top playmakers of the weekend.
